{"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/IronUI\/documentation\/IronUI\/Accessibility"},"kind":"article","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/ironui\/accessibility"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"abstract":[{"text":"Build inclusive interfaces with IronUI’s accessibility features.","type":"text"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/IronUI\/documentation\/IronUI"]]},"seeAlsoSections":[{"generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/IronUI\/documentation\/IronUI\/GettingStarted","doc:\/\/IronUI\/documentation\/IronUI\/Theming"],"anchor":"Essentials","title":"Essentials"}],"metadata":{"title":"Accessibility","modules":[{"name":"IronUI"}],"roleHeading":"Article","role":"article"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Overview","anchor":"Overview","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"IronUI is built with accessibility as a core principle. Every component supports VoiceOver, Dynamic Type, and reduced motion preferences out of the box."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"anchor":"VoiceOver-Support","type":"heading","text":"VoiceOver Support"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"All IronUI components provide meaningful accessibility labels and traits."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","text":"Automatic Labeling","level":3,"anchor":"Automatic-Labeling"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Components automatically generate appropriate labels:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ Automatically announces \"Primary button, Submit\"","IronButton(\"Submit\", variant: .filled) { }","","\/\/ Announces \"Toggle, Enable notifications, On\"","IronToggle(\"Enable notifications\", isOn: $isEnabled)","","\/\/ Announces \"Avatar for John Doe, Online\"","IronAvatar(name: \"John Doe\", status: .online)"]},{"level":3,"text":"Custom Labels","type":"heading","anchor":"Custom-Labels"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Override default labels when needed:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["IronButton(\"\", variant: .filled, leadingIcon: \"plus\") { }","    .accessibilityLabel(\"Add new item\")","","IronIcon(systemName: \"star.fill\", color: .warning)","    .accessibilityLabel(\"Favorite\")"]},{"level":3,"text":"Composite Elements","type":"heading","anchor":"Composite-Elements"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"IronUI combines related elements for efficient VoiceOver navigation:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ Chip with icon + label + dismiss = single VoiceOver element","IronChip(\"Swift\", icon: \"swift\") {","    \/\/ dismiss action","}","\/\/ Announces: \"Swift, Removable, Button. Actions available: Remove\""]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Dynamic-Type","level":2,"text":"Dynamic Type"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"IronUI scales appropriately with the user’s preferred text size."}]},{"level":3,"text":"Automatic Scaling","type":"heading","anchor":"Automatic-Scaling"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"All text and text-related measurements scale with Dynamic Type:"}]},{"code":["\/\/ Text automatically scales","IronText(\"Welcome\", style: .headlineLarge, color: .primary)","","\/\/ Icons scale proportionally","IronIcon(systemName: \"star\", size: .medium, color: .primary)","","\/\/ Spacing adapts to maintain visual balance","IronButton(\"Submit\", size: .large) { }"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"level":3,"type":"heading","text":"ScaledMetric Usage","anchor":"ScaledMetric-Usage"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Components use "},{"code":"@ScaledMetric","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" for consistent scaling:"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["struct MyComponent: View {","    @ScaledMetric(relativeTo: .body) private var iconSize: CGFloat = 20","","    var body: some View {","        Image(systemName: \"star\")","            .frame(width: iconSize, height: iconSize)","    }","}"]},{"level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Testing Dynamic Type","anchor":"Testing-Dynamic-Type"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Test your interfaces across the full range of sizes:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Extra Small"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" - Smallest readable size","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Large","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" - System default"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"XXX-Large"}]},{"type":"text","text":" - Large text preference"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Accessibility XXX-Large"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" - Maximum accessibility size"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Reduced Motion","anchor":"Reduced-Motion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"IronUI respects the user’s reduced motion preference.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","text":"Automatic Adaptation","level":3,"anchor":"Automatic-Adaptation"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Animations automatically simplify when reduced motion is enabled:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ Uses spring animation normally, instant transition with reduced motion","IronButton(\"Tap me\") { }","","\/\/ Progress spinner stops animated when reduced motion is on","IronSpinner()"]},{"type":"heading","text":"Manual Checking","anchor":"Manual-Checking","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Check the preference manually for custom animations:","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["struct MyView: View {","    @Environment(\\.accessibilityReduceMotion) private var reduceMotion","","    var body: some View {","        content","            .animation(reduceMotion ? nil : .spring(), value: isExpanded)","    }","}"]},{"level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Accessible Animation Modifier","anchor":"Accessible-Animation-Modifier"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"accessibleAnimation"},{"type":"text","text":" modifier for automatic handling:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["MyView()","    .accessibleAnimation(.bouncy, value: isExpanded)"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"type":"heading","text":"Color and Contrast","anchor":"Color-and-Contrast","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"IronUI’s semantic colors maintain WCAG contrast ratios."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","text":"Semantic Colors","anchor":"Semantic-Colors","level":3},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Always use semantic color tokens:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["\/\/ Good: Semantic colors adapt to context","IronText(\"Error message\", style: .bodyMedium, color: .error)","","\/\/ Avoid: Hardcoded colors may not have sufficient contrast","Text(\"Error\").foregroundColor(.red)"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"level":3,"type":"heading","text":"High Contrast Mode","anchor":"High-Contrast-Mode"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Components automatically enhance contrast when the user enables high contrast mode in system settings."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Best Practices","anchor":"Best-Practices"},{"type":"heading","text":"Do","level":3,"anchor":"Do"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Use descriptive labels that convey purpose","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Test with VoiceOver enabled"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Verify layouts at 